        "start": 4,
        "end": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "遵慶亦出為郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 20,
        "end": 26
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_113_000107",
    "sentence": "肅宗即位，征拜給事中、尚書右丞、吏部侍郎。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "尚書",
        "label": "TITLE",
